overview.en: ETP is a token of public welfare issued by Hutsadin elephant Foundation, which aims to appeal people to provide more public welfare protection activities for elephant rescue through block chain
overview.zh: ETP是由哈撒丁大象基金会Hutsadin Elephant Foundation发行的一款具有公益性质的token, 目的是为了通过区块链呼吁人们为大象的救援提供更多的公益性保护活动
